description:
Watch The Resurrected Life: Understanding the Meaning of Easter Episode 1 Crucifixion on Vision Video

Go beyond the story and symbols of Christianity! Artistic images of the Holy Land, soul-stirring music, and the wisdom of prominent spiritual leaders from various Christian traditions guide viewers of all walks of life and invite them to encounter God by peering into the core mystery of the faith. This first episode focuses on the crucifixion. 

Filled with artistic images of the Holy Land, soul-stirring music, and the wisdom of prominent spiritual teachers from various Christian traditions, The Resurrected Life is a feast for the mind, heart, and eyes. It offers practical insight into the transformational aspects of the Resurrection on a personal, intimate level that can affect profound changes in individual lives. The viewer is taken beyond the story and symbols into the spiritual awakening that is offered to every Christian who seeks to know God and live from that ever-deepening consciousness. This four-part program is designed for viewers of all walks of life who hunger for encounter with God, who seek paths of personal transformation and renewal, or who yearn for deeper insight into the core mystery of Christianity. It will inform, inspire and enlighten anyone who is interested in the spiritual journey.
